---
const base = '/plain-act';
const videos = [
  { title: 'How New Managers Build Authority Without Acting Tough', url: 'https://youtu.be/DuvDEIQwi3g', thumb: 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/DuvDEIQwi3g/hqdefault.jpg' },
  { title: 'Why New Managers Overexplain', url: 'https://youtu.be/ZC7cIHJPhho', thumb: 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZC7cIHJPhho/hqdefault.jpg' },
  { title: 'How New Managers Delegate Without Taking the Work Back', url: 'https://youtu.be/oWsC7tHsI38', thumb: 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/oWsC7tHsI38/hqdefault.jpg' }
];
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <meta name="description" content="Plain Act publishes quiet management manuals for first-time managers carrying authority under pressure." />
  <title>Plain Act | Quiet management manuals</title>
  <style>
    :root{--ink:#111315;--ink2:#1b1d1f;--paper:#f3f0e9;--muted:#aaa9a5;--line:#343638;--blue:#47687a;--max:1480px}
    *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}body{margin:0;background:var(--ink);color:#f7f5f0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif}a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}img{display:block;max-width:100%}
    .wrap{width:min(var(--max),calc(100% - 48px));margin:auto}
    header{height:84px;border-bottom:1px solid #282a2c;background:#101214;display:flex;align-items:center;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:20}
    .nav{display:grid;grid-template-columns:260px 1fr 80px;align-items:center;gap:24px}.brand{letter-spacing:.28em;font-size:22px}.brand small{display:block;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.42em;margin-top:7px;color:#aaa}
    nav{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:46px;font-size:15px}nav a{padding:31px 0 25px;border-bottom:2px solid transparent}nav a:first-child{border-color:#eee}.icons{text-align:right;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:13px}
    .hero{min-height:540px;background:radial-gradient(circle at 70% 25%,#2a2b2b 0,#17191a 38%,#111315 72%);overflow:hidden}.hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:48% 52%;min-height:540px;align-items:center}
    h1{font-size:clamp(42px,4.1vw,70px);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.035em;margin:0 0 24px;max-width:720px;font-weight:500}.rule{width:42px;height:2px;background:#c8c4bc;margin:24px 0}.lead{font-size:21px;line-height:1.55;color:#bbb;max-width:610px}
    .buttons{display:flex;gap:18px;margin:32px 0}.btn{padding:18px 34px;border:1px solid #d6d2cb;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;font-size:13px}.btn.primary{background:#f3f0e9;color:#17191a}.benefits{display:flex;gap:32px;margin-top:30px;color:#ccc;font-size:12px}.benefits span{padding-left:25px;position:relative}.benefits span:before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;border:1px solid #aaa;border-radius:50%;width:18px;height:18px;text-align:center;line-height:17px}
    .books{height:100%;position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-end;padding-bottom:22px}.plinth{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;height:78px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#3a3937,#242526);transform:perspective(500px) rotateX(8deg);box-shadow:0 -12px 30px #0008}
    .book{position:relative;z-index:2;filter:drop-shadow(24px 24px 22px #0009)}.book img{height:450px;width:auto}.book.dark{transform:translateX(58px) translateY(-12px);z-index:3}.book.light{transform:translateX(20px) translateY(5px);z-index:2}.book:after{content:'';position:absolute;right:-18px;top:8px;width:18px;height:calc(100% - 14px);background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,#b8b3a9 0 1px,#ddd8ce 1px 3px);transform:skewY(-5deg);transform-origin:left}
    .content-strip{background:var(--paper);color:#191b1d;border-top:1px solid #aaa;padding:28px 0}.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:0}.card{padding:0 34px;border-right:1px solid #d5d1ca}.card:first-child{padding-left:0}.card:last-child{border:0}.eyebrow{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.08em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:18px}.card-body{display:grid;grid-template-columns:190px 1fr;gap:20px;align-items:start}.card img{height:125px;width:190px;object-fit:cover;background:#222}.card h2{font-size:18px;margin:5px 0 12px}.card p{font-size:14px;line-height:1.45;color:#555}.more{font-size:13px;margin-top:14px;display:inline-block}
    .videos{padding:70px 0;background:#151719}.section-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:end;margin-bottom:30px}.section-head h2{font-size:36px;margin:0}.section-head p{color:#aaa;margin:0}.video-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px}.video-card{border:1px solid #333;background:#1d1f21}.video-card img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover}.video-card h3{font-size:18px;line-height:1.35;padding:18px;margin:0}.footer-top{background:#282a2c;padding:25px 0}.principles{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);color:#bbb}.principles div{padding:8px 30px;border-right:1px solid #494b4d}.principles div:last-child{border:0}.principles strong{display:block;color:#eee;margin-bottom:5px}.footer{padding:34px 0;color:#aaa;font-size:13px}.footer-inner{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:30px;flex-wrap:wrap}.footer a{margin-left:20px}
    @media(max-width:980px){.nav{grid-template-columns:1fr auto}.icons{display:none}nav{gap:18px;justify-content:end}.hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.hero{padding-top:55px}.books{min-height:460px}.cards,.video-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.card{border-right:0;border-bottom:1px solid #d5d1ca;padding:28px 0}.principles{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.book img{height:390px}}
    @media(max-width:650px){header{height:auto;padding:20px 0}.nav{display:block}.brand{margin-bottom:18px}nav{justify-content:flex-start;overflow:auto;gap:22px}nav a{padding:5px 0}.wrap{width:min(100% - 28px,var(--max))}.hero-grid{display:block}.hero-copy{padding:50px 0 20px}.buttons,.benefits{flex-direction:column}.books{min-height:390px;transform:scale(.82);transform-origin:center bottom}.book img{height:330px}.book.dark{transform:translateX(45px)}.book.light{transform:translateX(3px)}.card-body{grid-template-columns:130px 1fr}.card img{width:130px;height:100px}.principles{grid-template-columns:1fr}.principles div{border-right:0;border-bottom:1px solid #494b4d}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<header><div class="wrap nav"><a class="brand" href={`${base}/`}>PLAIN ACT<small>PUBLISHING</small></a><nav><a href={`${base}/`}>Home</a><a href={`${base}/books/`}>Books</a><a href={`${base}/articles/`}>Articles</a><a href={`${base}/resources/`}>Resources</a><a href={`${base}/about/`}>About</a><a href={`${base}/contact/`}>Contact</a></nav><div class="icons"> </div></div></header>
<main>
<section class="hero"><div class="wrap hero-grid"><div class="hero-copy"><h1>Quiet management manuals for people carrying authority under pressure.</h1><div class="rule"></div><p class="lead">Practical guidance for first-time managers who want to lead with clarity, not noise.</p><div class="buttons"><a class="btn primary" href={`${base}/books/the-first-30-days-as-a-new-manager/`}>View the books </a><a class="btn" href={`${base}/resources/`}>Explore resources</a></div><div class="benefits"><span>Practical<br><small>Real-world tools</small></span><span>For First-Time Managers<br><small>Written for where you are</small></span><span>Clear. Calm. Useful.<br><small>No jargon. No fluff.</small></span></div></div><div class="books"><div class="plinth"></div><div class="book dark"><img src={`${base}/images/hardcover-dark.png`} alt="Dark hardcover edition of The First 30 Days as a New Manager" /></div><div class="book light"><img src={`${base}/images/paperback-light.png`} alt="Light paperback edition of The First 30 Days as a New Manager" /></div></div></div></section>

<!-- PLAIN-ACT-BUY-SECTION -->
<section id="buy-now" class="buy-section" aria-labelledby="buy-title">
  <div class="buy-shell">
    <div class="buy-header">
      <p class="buy-kicker">BUY NOW</p>
      <h2 id="buy-title">Pick your edition and start reading.</h2>
      <p>Choose the format that works best for you. Google Play is shown first, followed by Kindle and the print editions on Amazon.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="buy-grid">
      <a class="buy-card buy-cheapest" href="https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=XafyEQAAQBAJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="buy-badge">LOWEST PRICE</span>
        <span class="buy-format">Google Play eBook</span>
        <strong>BUY NOW</strong>
        <span class="buy-note">View on Google Play &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a class="buy-card buy-primary" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GNSXZP21" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="buy-badge">$4.99 USD</span>
        <span class="buy-format">Kindle eBook</span>
        <strong>BUY NOW</strong>
        <span class="buy-note">View on Amazon &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a class="buy-card" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H5WHFLYY" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="buy-badge">$12.99 USD</span>
        <span class="buy-format">Paperback</span>
        <strong>BUY NOW</strong>
        <span class="buy-note">View on Amazon &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a class="buy-card" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H5WPDTNB" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="buy-badge">$18.99 USD</span>
        <span class="buy-format">Hardcover</span>
        <strong>BUY NOW</strong>
        <span class="buy-note">View on Amazon &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .buy-section {
    padding: clamp(42px, 5vw, 72px) 24px;
    background: #081420;
    color: #f6f1e7;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }
  .buy-shell {
    width: min(1180px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .buy-header {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .buy-kicker {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #e3b768;
    font-size: .78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: .16em;
  }
  .buy-header h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -.04em;
    color: #f7f3ea;
  }
  .buy-header p:not(.buy-kicker) {
    margin: 0;
    color: #b8c4cf;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .buy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .buy-card {
    display: flex;
    min-height: 180px;
    padding: 22px;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: #0d2236;
    color: #f7f3e9;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 38px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
    transition: transform .2s ease, border-color .2s ease, background .2s ease;
  }
  .buy-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: #e3b768;
    background: #112941;
  }
  .buy-card.buy-cheapest {
    background: #f2eadc;
    color: #081420;
    border-color: #f2eadc;
  }
  .buy-card.buy-cheapest:hover {
    background: #fff6e7;
  }
  .buy-card.buy-primary {
    border-color: rgba(227,183,104,.5);
  }
  .buy-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    width: fit-content;
    padding: 7px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: .75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }
  .buy-card.buy-cheapest .buy-badge {
    background: rgba(8,20,32,.08);
  }
  .buy-format {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: .95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .02em;
    opacity: .86;
  }
  .buy-card strong {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: .02em;
  }
  .buy-note {
    font-size: .92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    opacity: .92;
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .buy-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .buy-section { padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px; }
    .buy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .buy-card { min-height: 155px; }
  }
</style>

<section class="content-strip"><div class="wrap cards"><article class="card"><div class="eyebrow"> &nbsp; FEATURED ARTICLES </div><div class="card-body"><img src={`${base}/images/home-article.jpg`} alt="Notebook and pen" /><div><h2>The First 30 Days: Why They Set the Tone</h2><p>How early decisions shape trust, momentum, and your credibility.</p><a class="more" href={`${base}/articles/`}>Read Article </a></div></div></article><article class="card"><div class="eyebrow"> &nbsp; RELATED RESOURCES </div><div class="card-body"><img src={`${base}/images/home-resource.jpg`} alt="Manager checklist" /><div><h2>30-Day Manager Kickstart Checklist</h2><p>A practical day-by-day guide to help you start strong.</p><a class="more" href={`${base}/resources/`}>Explore Resources </a></div></div></article><article class="card"><div class="eyebrow"> &nbsp; FROM OUR YOUTUBE </div><div class="card-body"><img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/DuvDEIQwi3g/hqdefault.jpg" alt="Latest Plain Act video" /><div><h2>How New Managers Build Authority</h2><p>Build authority without acting tough or pretending to know everything.</p><a class="more" href="https://youtu.be/DuvDEIQwi3g">Watch on YouTube </a></div></div></article></div></section>
<section class="videos"><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><div><h2>From Plain Act on YouTube</h2><p>Practical management for people doing the job for real.</p></div><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Plan-Act">View channel </a></div><div class="video-grid">{videos.map(v=><a class="video-card" href={v.url}><img src={v.thumb} alt={v.title}/><h3>{v.title}</h3></a>)}</div></div></section>
<section class="footer-top"><div class="wrap principles"><div><strong>You dont need to be perfect.</strong>You just need a plan.</div><div><strong>Thoughtful Books</strong>Built for real work.</div><div><strong>Human-Focused</strong>Leadership is personal.</div><div><strong>Practical by Design</strong>Use it. Share it. Keep it close.</div></div></section>

</main>
<footer class="footer"><div class="wrap footer-inner"><span> 2026 PlainAct Publishing</span><span><a href={`${base}/affiliate-disclosure/`}>Affiliate Disclosure</a><a href={`${base}/privacy-policy/`}>Privacy Policy</a><a href={`${base}/sitemap/`}>Sitemap</a></span></div></footer>
</body></html>
